    dc:title "Two new Cnemaspis Strauch, 1887 (Squamata: Gekkonidae) from the Shevaroy massif, Tamil Nadu, India, with a preliminary ND 2 phylogeny of Indian Cnemaspis" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3150663>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3150675>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3150685>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3150692>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3150696>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3368371>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3150704> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3150663>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Photos in life of (A) Cnemaspis yercaudensis, male NCBS-BH678, (B) Cnemaspis yercaudensis, female BNHS 2534, (C) Cnemaspis thackerayi sp. nov., holotype male NCBS-BH670, (D) Cnemaspis thackerayi sp. nov., female, uncollected individual, (E) Cnemaspis shevaroyensis sp. nov., holotype male NCBS-BH674, (F) Cnemaspis shevaroyensis sp. nov., paratype female BNHS 2529; all from Yercaud on the Shevaroy massif, Salem district, Tamil Nadu, India." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3150663/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3150675>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Details of dorsal pholidosis at midbody of (A) Cnemaspis thackerayi sp. nov., holotype, NCBS-BH670, (C) Cnemaspis shevaroyensis sp. nov., holotype, NCBS-BH674 and details of ventral scales at midbody (B) Cnemaspis thackerayi sp. nov., holotype, NCBS-BH670, and (D) Cnemaspis shevaroyensis sp. nov., holotype, NCBS-BH674. Scale bars 5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3150675/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3150685>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Cnemaspis shevaroyensis sp. nov. (holotype, NCBS-BH674), dorsal view (A), ventral view (B), dorsal view of tail (C), and ventral view of tail (D). Scale bars 10 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3150685/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3150692>
    dc:description "FIGURE 9. Cnemaspis shevaroyensis sp. nov. (holotype, NCBS-BH674), dorsal view of head (A), ventral view of head (B), lateral view of head (C), view of cloacal region showing precloacal and femoral pores (D), ventral view of right manus (E), and ventral view of right pes (F). Scale bars 5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3150692/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3150696>
    dc:description "FIGURE 10. Type series of Cnemaspis shevaroyensis sp. nov. (from left to right, NCBS-BH675, NCBS-BH676, BNHS 2529, BNHS 2530 and BNHS 2531). Scale bar 10 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3150696/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3368371>
    dc:description "FIGURE. 1. Relief map showing distribution of four divergent Cnemaspis lineages in the Shevaroy massif and Kollimalai. Inset map of India shows location of study area (black rectangle)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3368371/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3150704>
    dc:description "FIGURE 11. Habitat photos of (A) Cnemaspis yercaudensis, (B) Cnemaspis thackerayi sp. nov., and (C) Cnemaspis shevaroyenesis sp. nov., from the Shevaroy massif, Salem district, Tamil Nadu, India." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3150704/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

